metadata.name: The intangible sensation of feeling everything.
metadata.description:
The intangible sensation of feeling everything, everywhere, forever. 

acrylic and oil painting on 24" 48" canvas.

The buyer of this NFT will receive the physical painting shipped to them. Contact and shipping info will be exchanged via PM or through my email - ansontknopp@gmail.com
